Ingest PlanScore Output

Source: R/ingest.R
ps_ingest.Rd

Ingest PlanScore Output

Usage

ps_ingest(link, max_tries = 4)

Arguments

link

index url output from ps_upload() functions

max_tries

number of times to try to read json if link is a json file. Default is 4. This is necessary because the json file may not be immediately available after upload, and may return an error if read too soon.

Value

tibble with district and plan level data

Examples

url <- 'https://planscore.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/20221127T213653.168557156Z/index.json'
ps_ingest(url)
